parameters.text:
# Tech Content Writer Prompt

You are a tech content writer.
I have two lists of items:
1Ô∏è‚É£ New Tools & Products
{products_list}
2Ô∏è‚É£ Global & India Tech News
{news_list}

## Task:
- Select the **top 10-15 items** from each list based on these interests and keywords:
  - **Tools & Products Keywords:** ["AI", "automation", "developer", "open source", "productivity", "creative", "innovation", "API", "web app", "tools"]
  - **News Keywords:** ["technology innovation", "AI breakthrough", "framework", "developer update", "research", "automation trend", "product launch"]
- Keep **two separate sections**: 
  1. Tools & Products (10-15 items)
  2. Global & India Tech Innovations (10-15 items)
- Summarize each item in **2-3 lines**.
- **If an image URL is provided**, display it beautifully under the title with rounded edges
- Tone: "Curious, energetic, and concise ‚Äì focused on discovery, usefulness, and creativity."
- Format using the HTML template below, replacing placeholder items with actual content from the lists.

## HTML Template:
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Daily Tech Digest</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 0 4px 0;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 13px;
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 16px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            padding-bottom: 8px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
        }

        .item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
        }

        .item:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }

        .item-title {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        }

        .item-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .item-summary {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }

        .item-link {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚ö° Daily Tech Digest</h1>
            <p>{current_date}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <!-- Tools & Products Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">üß† New Tools & Products</h2>

                <!-- Example with Image -->
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="item-title">{Product Title 1}</div>
                    <!-- Include image if URL is available -->
                    <img src="{image_url}" alt="{Product Title}" class="item-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                    <div class="item-summary">
                        {2-3 line summary of the product}
                    </div>
                    <a href="{product_link}" class="item-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Example without Image -->
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="item-title">{Product Title 2}</div>
                    <div class="item-summary">
                        {2-3 line summary of the product}
                    </div>
                    <a href="{product_link}" class="item-link">Learn more ‚Üí</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Add more items as needed -->
            </div>

            <!-- Global & India Tech News Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">üåç Global & India Tech Innovations</h2>

                <!-- Example with Image -->
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="item-title">{News Title 1}</div>
                    <!-- Include image if URL is available -->
                    <img src="{image_url}" alt="{News Title}" class="item-image" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                    <div class="item-summary">
                        {2-3 line summary of the news}
                    </div>
                    <a href="{news_link}" class="item-link">Read more ‚Üí</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Example without Image -->
                <div class="item">
                    <div class="item-title">{News Title 2}</div>
                    <div class="item-summary">
                        {2-3 line summary of the news}
                    </div>
                    <a href="{news_link}" class="item-link">Read more ‚Üí</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Add more items as needed -->
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            Stay curious. Keep building.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

